?
Monaka...? Why do you have this?

I received it just now.
I was told to eat it with Fuyuko-chan.

Nah,
I got it from some grandpa.

Who... umm. He was wearing a kimono...
and he was in the green room 3 rooms back from here.

Aaa～......! I've told you not to go causing 
trouble for other people, right...?!

We were just talking a bit!
And at some point in the there he gave them to me!

～～tch, Alright, alright. Whatever...
For now we'll go introduce ourselves to him. Together...!
